-- Validus Raises $404.4 Million in Capital For Insurance Wagers
-- B y   E l i z a b e t h   B u n n
-- 2013-01-09T22:28:37Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-01-09/validus-raises-404-4-million-in-capital-for-insurance-wagers.html
Validus Holdings Ltd., the reinsurer
that acquired Flagstone Reinsurance Holdings SA, said an
investment advisory subsidiary raised $404.4 million of third-
party capital.  The funds will be used for investment in collateralized
coverage and insurance-linked securities, Bermuda-based Validus
said today in a statement distributed by Business Wire.  To contact the reporter on this story:
